{
  "video_id": "TUgBd-yK7-4",
  "title": "What soccer can teach us about freedom | Marc Bamuthi Joseph",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12880.0,
      "end_time": 16960.0,
      "text": "The two places"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16120.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19600.0,
      "text": "where I feel most free"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20680.0,
      "end_time": 22936.0,
      "text": "aren&#39;t actually places."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22960.0,
      "end_time": 24400.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re moments."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25640.0,
      "end_time": 28760.0,
      "text": "The first is inside of dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29360.0,
      "end_time": 32576.0,
      "text": "Somewhere between rising up against gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32600.0,
      "end_time": 36960.0,
      "text": "and the feeling that the air beneath me"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36120.0,
      "end_time": 38800.0,
      "text": "is falling in love with my body&#39;s weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39760.0,
      "end_time": 43696.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m dancing and the air is carrying me"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43720.0,
      "end_time": 45440.0,
      "text": "like I might never come down."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46920.0,
      "end_time": 48776.0,
      "text": "The second place that I feel free"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 51896.0,
      "text": "is after scoring a goal on the soccer pitch."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51920.0,
      "end_time": 54536.0,
      "text": "My body floods with the chemical"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54560.0,
      "end_time": 57656.0,
      "text": "that they put inside of EpiPens to revive the dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57680.0,
      "end_time": 60720.0,
      "text": "and I am weightless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61440.0,
      "end_time": 63480.0,
      "text": "raceless."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64840.0,
      "end_time": 68896.0,
      "text": "My story is this: I&#39;m a curator at a contemporary arts center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68920.0,
      "end_time": 75200.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t really believe in art that doesn&#39;t bleed or sweat or cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76000.0,
      "end_time": 78616.0,
      "text": "I imagine that my kids are going to live in a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78640.0,
      "end_time": 82720.0,
      "text": "when the most valuable commodities are fresh water and empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83560.0,
      "end_time": 85976.0,
      "text": "I love pretty dances and majestic sculpture"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86000.0,
      "end_time": 87656.0,
      "text": "as much as the next guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87680.0,
      "end_time": 89880.0,
      "text": "but give me something else to go with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90480.0,
      "end_time": 93136.0,
      "text": "Lift me up with the aesthetic sublime"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 97856.0,
      "text": "and give me a practice or some tools to turn that inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97880.0,
      "end_time": 99960.0,
      "text": "into understanding and action."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101160.0,
      "end_time": 106136.0,
      "text": "For instance, I&#39;m a theater maker who loves sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106160.0,
      "end_time": 108416.0,
      "text": "When I was making my latest piece /peh-LO-tah/"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108440.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "I thought a lot about how soccer was a means for my own immigrant family"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 117896.0,
      "text": "to foster a sense of continuity and normality and community"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117920.0,
      "end_time": 120360.0,
      "text": "within the new context of the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121240.0,
      "end_time": 126295.0,
      "text": "In this heightened moment of xenophobia and assault on immigrant identity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126320.0,
      "end_time": 127895.0,
      "text": "I wanted to think through"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 127920.0,
      "end_time": 131976.0,
      "text": "how the game could serve as an affirmational tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132000.0,
      "end_time": 135496.0,
      "text": "for first-generation Americans and immigrant kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 138936.0,
      "text": "to ask them to consider movement patterns on the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 138960.0,
      "end_time": 144240.0,
      "text": "as kin to migratory patterns across social and political borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144880.0,
      "end_time": 146376.0,
      "text": "Whether footballers or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 146400.0,
      "end_time": 149880.0,
      "text": "immigrants in the US play on endangered ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 150880.0,
      "end_time": 152736.0,
      "text": "I wanted to help the kids understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 152760.0,
      "end_time": 156616.0,
      "text": "that the same muscle that they use to plan the next goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156640.0,
      "end_time": 159799.0,
      "text": "can also be used to navigate the next block."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 161160.0,
      "end_time": 164680.0,
      "text": "For me, freedom exists in the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 165240.0,
      "end_time": 168160.0,
      "text": "We talk about it abstractly and even divisively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 168400.0,
      "end_time": 171816.0,
      "text": "like \"protect our freedom,\" \"build this wall,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 171840.0,
      "end_time": 173840.0,
      "text": "\"they hate us because of our freedom.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174400.0,
      "end_time": 177816.0,
      "text": "We have all these systems that are beautifully designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 177840.0,
      "end_time": 180536.0,
      "text": "to incarcerate us or deport us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180560.0,
      "end_time": 183600.0,
      "text": "but how do we design freedom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 184680.0,
      "end_time": 188856.0,
      "text": "For these kids, I wanted to track the idea back to something that exists inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 188880.0,
      "end_time": 190256.0,
      "text": "that no one could take away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190280.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "so I developed this curriculum"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192400.0,
      "end_time": 196976.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s part poli-sci class, part soccer tournament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 197000.0,
      "end_time": 199440.0,
      "text": "inside of an arts festival."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 203896.0,
      "text": "It accesses /peh-LO-tah/&#39;s field of inquiry"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 203920.0,
      "end_time": 207815.0,
      "text": "to create a sports-based political action for young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 207840.0,
      "end_time": 210536.0,
      "text": "The project is called \"Moving and Passing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 210560.0,
      "end_time": 214696.0,
      "text": "It intersects curriculum development, site-specific performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 214720.0,
      "end_time": 216616.0,
      "text": "and the politics of joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 216640.0,
      "end_time": 220775.0,
      "text": "while using soccer as a metaphor for the urgent question"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 220800.0,
      "end_time": 223160.0,
      "text": "of enfranchisement among immigrant youth."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 224120.0,
      "end_time": 227896.0,
      "text": "Imagine that you are a 15-year-old kid from Honduras"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227920.0,
      "end_time": 229696.0,
      "text": "now living in Harlem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 229720.0,
      "end_time": 234616.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re a 13-year-old girl born in DC to two Nigerian immigrants."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234640.0,
      "end_time": 235976.0,
      "text": "You love the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236000.0,
      "end_time": 237816.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re on the field with your folks."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237840.0,
      "end_time": 240256.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve just been practicing dribbling through cones"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 240280.0,
      "end_time": 241536.0,
      "text": "for, like, 15 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241560.0,
      "end_time": 245440.0,
      "text": "and then, all of a sudden, a marching band comes down the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246360.0,
      "end_time": 251960.0,
      "text": "I want to associate the joy of the game with the exuberance of culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251120.0,
      "end_time": 255616.0,
      "text": "to locate the site of joy in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255640.0,
      "end_time": 258176.0,
      "text": "at the same physical coordinate"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258200.0,
      "end_time": 262550.0,
      "text": "as being politically informed by art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262790.0,
      "end_time": 265440.0,
      "text": "a grass-laden theater for liberation."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 265840.0,
      "end_time": 267560.0,
      "text": "We spend a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 267800.0,
      "end_time": 270616.0,
      "text": "looking at how the midfielder would explain Black Lives Matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270640.0,
      "end_time": 273815.0,
      "text": "or how the goalkeeper would explain gun control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273839.0,
      "end_time": 278160.0,
      "text": "or how a defender&#39;s style is the perfect metaphor"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 278400.0,
      "end_time": 280776.0,
      "text": "for the limits of American exceptionalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 282856.0,
      "text": "As we study positions on the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 282880.0,
      "end_time": 287000.0,
      "text": "we also name and imagine our own freedoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 288720.0,
      "end_time": 290456.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know, man, soccer is, like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 290480.0,
      "end_time": 295160.0,
      "text": "the only thing on this planet that we can all agree to do together."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 295400.0,
      "end_time": 299160.0,
      "text": "You know? It&#39;s like the official sport of this spinning ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 300000.0,
      "end_time": 305960.0,
      "text": "I want to be able to connect the joy of the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 305120.0,
      "end_time": 308376.0,
      "text": "to the ever-moving footballer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308400.0,
      "end_time": 310536.0,
      "text": "to connect that moving footballer"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 310560.0,
      "end_time": 315400.0,
      "text": "to immigrants who also moved in sight of a better position."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 315720.0,
      "end_time": 319376.0,
      "text": "Among these kids, I want to connect their families&#39; histories"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 319400.0,
      "end_time": 322560.0,
      "text": "to the bliss of a goal-scorer&#39;s run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 322800.0,
      "end_time": 326960.0,
      "text": "family like that feeling after the ball beats the goalie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 326120.0,
      "end_time": 329000.0,
      "text": "the closest thing going to freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330000.0,
      "end_time": 331216.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 331240.0,
      "end_time": 336720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}